    feat: reject Gemm operation when transpose or broadcast option are set (not supported yet)
---
 wonnx/src/compiler.rs | 15 +++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 15 insertions(+)

diff --git a/wonnx/src/compiler.rs b/wonnx/src/compiler.rs
index b04dd95..a083911 100644
